- **H031 / route-over-ComputerVersion remains violated.** Correctly Phase D/E work, not Phase A.
  - `docs/definitions/og-dolt-heresy-completion-2026-07-08.md:160-190`
- **D-STORE remains unresolved.** Correctly open and outside Phase A exit bar.
  - `docs/definitions/og-dolt-heresy-completion-2026-07-08.md:424-426`
- **Round-2 opencode logs-only status.** Correctly recorded; only round 1 and round 3 opencode verdicts are misrecorded.

